snippet.title: HAPPY MAN [ GUITAR FREAKS, PSX ]
snippet.description:
Not much to say...again...except this animation is actually quite a lot different to the ones in virtually every GFDM since.  There's a lot more 3D type stuff in this one.

To this day I wonder what's with "censored eyes man" in the background...for about 5 seconds...
